STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Aquil MALIK, a/k/a Malik Aquil, Defendant-Petitioner. C-1005 September Term 2018
082341 Supreme Court of New Jersey. JUNE 13, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002683-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
